# Local Development Components
# Pattern: src/component/*_local/ - Components with _local suffix for development/testing
# These are loaded by the runtime but ignored by git (never committed)
# See: .specify/specs/001-component-standard/spec.md - "Local development pattern (*_local)"
# Usage: Create cmp_XXXX_name_local/ to test without committing, rename to activate
# Note: Different from _cmp_* (disabled components) - _local loads, _cmp_* is ignored by runtime
/src/component/*_local/

**/custom-snippets.ntpl
